      <title>Hexo Blog Set Up</title>
      <link href="/2019/07/20/Hexo-Blog-Set-Up/"/>
      <url>/2019/07/20/Hexo-Blog-Set-Up/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Set up blog with Hexo, Next theme, github.</p><h2 id="Blog-set-up"><a href="#Blog-set-up" class="headerlink" title="Blog set up"></a>Blog set up</h2><h3 id="Install-Hexo"><a href="#Install-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="Install Hexo"></a>Install Hexo</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Create-blog-dir"><a href="#Create-blog-dir" class="headerlink" title="Create blog dir"></a>Create blog dir</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>After installation, _config.yml is important under dir. Basic setting of website, e.g., title, description, keywords, etc.<br>Finish config change, in blog dir, exec</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>local mode has been started. Can be accessed through <a href="http://localhost:4000" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://localhost:4000</a></p><h3 id="Integete-with-github"><a href="#Integete-with-github" class="headerlink" title="Integete with github"></a>Integete with github</h3><p>github provided github.io to enable website build. Create a public repo with your ${github_account}.github.io.</p><h4 id="addon-for-hexo"><a href="#addon-for-hexo" class="headerlink" title="addon for hexo"></a>addon for hexo</h4><p>Install hexo-deployer-git.</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Configure your github repo in _config.yml</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">type</span>: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: https://github.com/Russell-W-Huang/russell-w-huang.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="deploy-blog-to-github-repo"><a href="#deploy-blog-to-github-repo" class="headerlink" title="deploy blog to github repo"></a>deploy blog to github repo</h4><p>exec</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Access-your-new-website"><a href="#Access-your-new-website" class="headerlink" title="Access your new website"></a>Access your new website</h2><p>Be exited to see website through https://${github_account}.github.io</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
